title: Rocco Legacy
description:
Autobiography of Jennifer Rocco and The Rocco Family. A tale of Alex Rocco finding redemption after being a member of the Winter Hill Gang, finding God and sharing his story of Family, love, loyalty faith and prisms of laughter through severe and mulitple tragedies.

The book represents The Rocco's and their struggles to find the light through the darknesses through pictures and pop culture.

A mafia/Hollywood verson of Forrest Gump, extolling hundreds of stories Ms. Rocco had met in her life. Through the eyes of love and faith. Hardships and triumphs. A book for the masses that have hit the economy in hard times. Ms. Rocco writes for them.
An attorney of 20 years, most of this book is based soley on eyewitness events and documetary documenation which is public.

Thank you for taking the journey into ROCOO FAMILY LEGACY. The next Family drama told in a soulful and faithful manner.

A memorial to the world for those that miss The Rocco Family's presence in this world
